snippet.title: Play my game! - SACRIFIGHTS
snippet.description:
Play SACRIFIGHTS here: https://frankiesmileshow.itch.io/sacrifight
Made for Ludum Dare 44. Art/Sounds/Voices by me. 
Programming by FrankiePixelShow. https://twitter.com/FrancisCoulombe
Music by cboyardee. https://twitter.com/cboyardee

SUBSCRIBE for more! 👉 http://bit.ly/subscribeLUMPY 👈
🔶Help me make more stuff like this: https://www.patreon.com/LumpyTouch
🦆Follow me on TWITTER: https://twitter.com/LumpyTouch
📷The Lumpy INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/lumpytouch/
📺Art Stream on TWITCH: https://www.twitch.tv/lumpytouch

SACRIFIGHTS is a boss rush game where you summon demons by sacrificing various objects. You can also consume disgusting organs to gain dark arcane energy. You have a week to get as powerful as possible before you battle an ancient evil.

Music:
Sonic 3 - File Select

#gaming #trailer #game
